{"tid":2140964,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Maps 街景功能擴至日本　支持東京、京都、名古屋及大阪","createTime":"2020-08-05T10:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T21:00:30.000Z","uid":9411,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4c419e5e50c4e5abc7ac90e52a0f89cc0f4ec4","tid":2140964,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:42:06.000Z","msg":"Google Street View 街景功能相信大家也很喜歡，而 Apple 在 iOS 13 開始加入 Look Around 功能，同樣能夠讓使用者看到街景。<br />\n<br />\n今天，Apple Maps 正式在日本加入這項 Look Around 功能，而首批加入的日本城市有 4 個，分别是東京、京都、名古屋及大阪。相信，對於喜歡日本的人來說，加入這項功能就能讓大家更輕鬆地「眼睛旅行」，方便規劃行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/08/05/apple-maps-japan-look-arround/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F08%2F05%2Fapple-maps-japan-look-arround%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeajvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=ed4571e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/08/05/apple-maps-japan-look-arround/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於可以去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5448062444c534ca278583a16a127d465294307","tid":2140964,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"幾時先有得VR行街？<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Map一格一格好無癮"},{"pid":"b3db2b6dc654cf781bf53116567c51f5a12c31a5","tid":2140964,"uid":257914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"支乜撚持"},{"pid":"33bae675956a1f6cf636d248464429ff81f2eed5","tid":2140964,"uid":9411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"預覽圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TyuvMX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F